snippet.title: Suikoden I&II HD Remaster Gate Rune and Dunan Unification Wars Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
"Suikoden I&II HD Remaster Gate Rune and Dunan Unification Wars" will be released on PlayStation®4, XBOX ONE, STEAM® and Nintendo Switch™.
